nodes.text: Sector 3263827 was a location that received refuse from Black Spire Outpost, a remote settlement on the planet Batuu in the Outer Rim Territories. Garbage receptacles in the outpost were stamped with orders, written in Aurebesh, to transport trash to the sector.

Sector 3263827 was first mentioned in Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge, which opened to guests at Disneyland Park on May 31, 2019. Many garbage and recycling cans in Disney's Star Wars-themed land have a label on them, written in Aurebesh, that reads "Trash to Sector 3263827." It is a reference to garbage masher 3263827, the garbage compactor that Princess Leia, Chewbacca, Luke Skywalker, and Han Solo escaped into during their escape from the Death Star in the 1977 film Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope.
